{
  "texts": [
    "Overall, preference datasets in languages other than English are relatively scarce.",
    "(6) Preference dataset examples mainly focus on general domains and social norm domains, especially in the realm of social norms.",
    "The primary goal is to ensure that LLMs align with human expectations across various general tasks and comprehensive safety considerations.",
    "Preference datasets specifically tailored for other vertical domains have not received significant attention at the moment.",
    "Evaluation datasets are a carefully curated and annotated set of data samples used to assess the performance of LLMs across various tasks."
  ]
}